                    <li>Underground cities that can hold thousands of people</li>
                    <li>Places to store weapons and supplies</li>
                </ul>

                <p>But experts in engineering say that building a 90-mile tunnel would be a huge challenge. The Gotthard Base Tunnel in Switzerland is the longest underground rail tunnel in the world. It is only 35.4 miles long and took more than ten years to build.</p>

